M|Step|tx|ds the first bd-Measure-Learn loop for the new direction. Do not bd a new pd. bd a new experiment.
M|Step|Give|typically 4-8 weeks to gather initial signal. If the new direction does not show promise within this window, reassess.
M|Step|it|Tell the team why the pivot is happening and what was learned
M|Step|it|up investors or sponsors w/ the new hypothesis
M|Step|- Re|pivots are not failures, they are evidence of learning
M|Calc|tx|**Pivot capacity** = (Remaining runway) / (Time per pivot cycle)
M|Calc|If y|
M|Calc|tx|Pivot capacity = 18 / 3 = 6 pivots remaining
M|Calc|tx|This means you can tst 6 fundamentally different hypotheses before running out of money. This number shd guide urgency.
M|Runw|tx|\| Runway Remaining \| Recommended Action \|
M|Runw|tx|\|-----------------\|--------------------\|
M|Runw|tx|\| 12+ months \| Full pivot exploration. tst new hypothesis thoroughly. \|
M|Runw|tx|\| 6-12 months \| Focused pivot. Must show signal within 8 weeks. \|
M|Runw|tx|\| 3-6 months \| Emergency pivot. Only pursue if signal is already visible. Consider bridge funding. \|
M|Runw|tx|\| Under 3 months \| Too late for a genuine pivot. Consider acqui-hire, asset sale, or wind-down. \|
M|Redu|it|Use faster MVP tp (smoke tst, concierge) instead of building pd
M|Redu|it|tst w/ smaller cs samples (10-20 instead of 100+)
M|Redu|it|Run parallel experiments on different pivot hypotheses
M|Redu|it|Use existing platforms and tools instead of custom dv
M|Redu|it|Set decision deadlines before starting
M|Post|Afte|
M|Post|it|[ ] New value hypothesis is clearly stated and different from the original
M|Post|it|[ ] First experiment for the new direction is designed and running within 2 weeks
M|Post|it|[ ] Baseline metrics for the new direction are established within 4 weeks
M|Post|it|[ ] At least 10 cs conversations validate the new problem/solution fit
M|Post|it|[ ] Team is aligned on the new direction and understands why the pivot happened
M|Post|it|[ ] Investors or sponsors are informed and supportive
M|Post|it|[ ] Old metrics dashboard is archived; new dashboard reflects new hypotheses
M|Post|it|[ ] Kill criteria for the new direction are defined (what wld cause another pivot)
M|Post|it|[ ] Runway is recalculated and pivot capacity is updated
M|Post|it|[ ] Learnings from the pre-pivot phase are documented and accessible
M|Post|tx|A pivot is not an admission of fl. It is the mechanism by which startups convert learning into st. The goal is not to avoid pivots but to execute them quickly, cheaply, and based on evidence.